# .NET build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/*.user
**/*.lscache

# Tests
tests/
**/*.Tests/
*.Tests.csproj.lscache

# Local config + secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets/
**/*.pfx
**/*.key
# appsettings.Development.json carries dev-only literal secrets
# (Keycloak/KeycloakAdmin client secrets, rustfsadmin DocumentStorage keys,
# postgres password). The runtime image runs with ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=Beta
# so the file is never loaded — exclude from the OCI image filesystem to
# avoid shipping the literals into the published GHCR image. Local dev uses
# `dotnet run` (not the Docker image) so no developer ergonomic impact.
**/appsettings.Development.json

# IDE / editor
**/.vs/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Source-control + planning artifacts (paths relative to repo root if `..` context is ever used)
.git/
.github/
_bmad-output/
_bmad/
docs/
